349
00:18:22,906 --> 00:18:24,724
Obrigado, Mike.

350
00:18:28,936 --> 00:18:30,836
Filho da mãe.

351
00:18:30,838 --> 00:18:34,323
Imagens de satélite mostram
o sexto exército russo

352
00:18:34,326 --> 00:18:36,026
